Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.21,0:01:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah, that's great!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.33,0:01:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,IT IS SERIOUS! MY MOTHER FELL
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.93,0:01:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's just fever!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.01,0:01:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I can go to work!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.50,0:01:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No! No!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.15,0:01:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I'm worried about the workflow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.40,0:01:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very important to relax\Nuntil you get better from fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.06,0:01:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.49,0:01:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You can miss another day, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.54,0:01:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.12,0:01:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's only for today...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.39,0:01:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.42,0:01:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch Sam well and don't let him get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.18,0:01:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, I understood, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.66,0:02:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm fine, Lassie...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.87,0:02:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Just feel a little bit dizzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.98,0:02:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.34,0:02:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, nothing, nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.95,0:02:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, you look tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.61,0:02:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You also came back late last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.08,0:02:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.77,0:02:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,All these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.95,0:02:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a bit tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.95,0:02:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I have lots of patients!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.71,0:02:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I need strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really fine, don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.93,0:02:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take care of your father!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.19,0:02:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.31,0:02:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.37,0:02:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Melissa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.01,0:02:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize but can you come later\Nto check on my family?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.37,0:03:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hasn't his temperature dropped yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.04,0:03:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.89,0:03:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.22,0:03:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How is your wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your concern!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, are you still going to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.27,0:03:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.25,0:03:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,My God, my God, it's rare\Nto be treated so harshly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.82,0:03:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you finish eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.05,0:03:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Many people have had cough...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.97,0:03:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,John... listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.66,0:03:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your mother is busy these days, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.02,0:03:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.67,0:03:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She's works too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.91,0:03:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,At these times you will be busy eating lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, fever is rampant anyway...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.07,0:03:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it's bad for her not to eat lunch.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.81,0:03:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.59,0:03:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring the lunch to my mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:03:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I feel fine now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.83,0:04:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if that's it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.58,0:04:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.43,0:04:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.09,0:04:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I will rest in peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.06,0:04:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And now go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.33,0:04:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this time I can help my mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.08,0:04:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hello!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.12,0:04:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.89,0:04:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.26,0:04:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It was very busy, but the place is empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,0:04:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.78,0:04:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,List of patients!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.26,0:04:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.35,0:04:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No more patient visits yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.46,0:04:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh!\N- Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.72,0:04:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, we...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I count on you to bring it\Nto the last floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.13,0:05:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And now won't hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.92,0:05:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But you should be cured of fever immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.03,0:05:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.27,0:05:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I want you to visit us again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.35,0:05:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- You'll get better quickly!\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.75,0:05:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's get to the next house!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.64,0:05:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Busy! Busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.88,0:05:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The pulse...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.96,0:05:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that way the heat will be gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.66,0:05:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, rest only!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.18,0:05:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.03,0:05:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- Here!\N- Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.18,0:05:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's at least I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.63,0:05:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But... my mom and the doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.46,0:05:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mom!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.76,0:05:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.78,0:06:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You forgot to take your lunch with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.26,0:06:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.86,0:06:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we'll be back here at five o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.56,0:06:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I must prepare medicines to\Nsend them to patients in need!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This is tiring!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.43,0:06:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All the people of this house are sick!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sorry, how is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.24,0:06:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's a little high.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Jake?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.46,0:06:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The father who was in this\Nhouse treated him first!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.11,0:06:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So you'll get better quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.74,0:06:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But we don't have enough fever medicines.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.34,0:06:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday I ordered other medicines.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it won't arrive quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.97,0:06:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,As recently as his students didn't get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it will arrive tomorrow afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.12,0:06:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,From here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:06:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I will go and bring it back...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.45,0:07:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Carraclough!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, she fell!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mom!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.73,0:07:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mom! Mom!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.98,0:07:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mom!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.64,0:07:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,John...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.09,0:07:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.69,0:07:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm the one who should apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.98,0:07:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I made you work so hard that it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I will wake up immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.08,0:07:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.41,0:07:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.16,0:07:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a little tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.43,0:07:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Patients are waiting for me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.24,0:07:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, your temperature is too high!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a medicine for fever!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.14,0:07:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This medicine is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.02,0:07:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.58,0:07:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's normal for patients with fever\Nto receive injection!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.81,0:08:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But the drugs will be delayed\Nuntil tomorrow afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Not until after the dawn of tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.97,0:08:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Rice went to pick it up by truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You can inject this medicine\Nafter the medication arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.24,0:08:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, I never want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.69,0:08:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The other patients need me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.28,0:08:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Carraclough!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.88,0:08:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Your stubbornness won't be\Nas effective today as yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.00,0:08:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.13,0:08:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.07,0:08:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.75,0:08:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sam, are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.50,0:08:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- Go to the front!\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.86,0:08:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We've heard that Mrs. Melissa\Nhas fallen unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.76,0:08:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Please enter!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.17,0:08:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I made soup for you,\Nso eat it and get better quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.49,0:09:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Melissa, everyone knows\Nyou're concerned about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.15,0:09:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So everyone in the village appreciates it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.95,0:09:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah! Yeah!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.10,0:09:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.88,0:09:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Melissa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Y--yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is in trouble now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.56,0:09:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,In the village there is one nurse,\Nshe worked hard until she fell!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.01,0:09:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma, don't say that,\Nyou better appreciate her feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.51,0:09:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Carraclough!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.81,0:09:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't the words of Grandma Forrest true?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.56,0:09:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better for you to get an injection to get\Nbetter, it's the desire of the people as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.35,0:09:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- Doctor!\N- That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.84,0:09:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,While you are at home, Mom,\NI will help Dr. Hooper!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,John...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.25,0:09:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.28,0:09:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what the syringe is,\Nbut you have to get better soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no one in your place!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.54,0:09:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mhm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.09,0:10:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.01,0:10:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother worked hard for everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! That's right, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.51,0:10:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.44,0:10:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave your wife to you, Sam!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Y-yes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.48,0:10:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Hooper!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.02,0:10:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.08,0:10:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, I mentioned earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.53,0:10:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.26,0:10:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.96,0:10:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard for you, doctor,\Nto work alone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.68,0:10:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not as good as my mother,\Nbut can't I help you with a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.81,0:10:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, even Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.85,0:10:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.68,0:10:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you say so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother was taking care of the patients too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.26,0:10:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.47,0:10:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.52,0:10:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I count on you, John! Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.89,0:10:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.11,0:11:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the lungs are okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.92,0:11:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}John, the tongue inhibitor!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Tongue inhibitor... yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.22,0:11:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Say "a"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Laryngoscopy!{\i0}\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.56,0:11:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, is that the binoculars?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hm!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.94,0:11:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.05,0:11:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.96,0:11:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got the tool names, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is next?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.86,0:11:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No 21, Mrs. Harrison!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.31,0:11:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.95,0:11:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.91,0:11:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.76,0:11:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Please get better quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We still have a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh my God, my God!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The number of medicines is many\Nand can't be counted!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I will deliver the next medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.86,0:11:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I count on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I will check the inventory now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.34,0:11:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if his temperature is low, he is\Nstill a person to be warned.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.22,0:12:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The man with fever never changes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.26,0:12:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Rice went to get the medicines,\NI hope he will return quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.27,0:12:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.38,0:12:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go back to the village quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That way I will never move!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.37,0:12:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I hate the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Dr. Hooper's medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.35,0:12:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.23,0:12:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, there's only one house left!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Gabel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Gabel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.03,0:12:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shut up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.55,0:12:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Open the door and come in!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.43,0:12:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let you in!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.22,0:12:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought your medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A child? What happened to Melissa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.56,0:12:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother is very sick,\Nthat's why I came instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.01,0:12:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:13:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's different from the usual\Nrheumatoid medication.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.89,0:13:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fever medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.17,0:13:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Please eat your full food!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.98,0:13:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.67,0:13:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm leaving now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.03,0:13:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.02,0:13:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Even food can't be eaten, as you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.12,0:13:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't move from bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.10,0:13:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You ask me to make food for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.47,0:13:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take this medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.71,0:13:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.35,0:13:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.56,0:13:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.98,0:13:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to start by washing dishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any pot to use!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any complaint?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.11,0:13:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Melissa always does that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.58,0:13:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.68,0:13:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, do this too...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I have finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm going now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.16,0:13:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.65,0:13:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.52,0:13:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you always come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.67,0:13:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You do this well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:13:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.17,0:14:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I will ask you to do so from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.78,0:14:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.23,0:14:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hooper!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He's walking fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.64,0:14:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.74,0:14:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Gabel, I have to go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Dr. Hooper has many patients!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.30,0:14:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I really have to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.58,0:14:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,xxx!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.88,0:14:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If you open the cabinet\Nyou will find a bottle shelf.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.90,0:14:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the special strawberry drink.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It have been very helpful to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.46,0:14:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why I should give Melissa this drink.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Melissa always looked after me\Nwithout grumbling.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mr. Gabel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.79,0:14:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I will come again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.23,0:14:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Hooper!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.85,0:14:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Jake's temperature has risen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.14,0:14:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, this boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It was worse because we weren't careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.39,0:15:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Aunt...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.98,0:15:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Jake okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.09,0:15:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What? He don't have pneumonia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.45,0:15:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If it doesn't get to the point he will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I will take care of him now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.66,0:15:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Aunt, you have to rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.16,0:15:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.48,0:15:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I will take care of Jake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.96,0:15:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Aunt, you have to recover your health quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.88,0:15:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get well, Auntie,\Nyou can take care of Jake!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.38,0:15:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now go back to your bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.42,0:15:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow morning when you recover
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.30,0:15:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,you can hug Jake as much as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.06,0:15:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.99,0:15:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.00,0:15:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How is his temperature?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.91,0:15:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.66,0:16:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The temperature is high.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Still high?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.85,0:16:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.58,0:16:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's just a fever,\Nso there's no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.87,0:16:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,His temperature can decrease\Nif we observe it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We must wait for Rice to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.72,0:16:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It broke at such a time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.77,0:16:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a lot of work!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.16,0:16:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The medicine hasn't arrived yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.70,0:16:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Doctor Hooper!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.97,0:16:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to the clinic and found the paper\Nwhere you wrote that you are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.69,0:16:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.14,0:16:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother's fever has increased again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.95,0:16:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take a look at her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.28,0:16:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all. I have to go to Olsen's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.21,0:16:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize but please take good care of Jake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.82,0:16:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If his temperature suddenly rises,\Ntell me immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.98,0:16:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.38,0:16:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, also don't forget to dry the towel again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.46,0:16:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes, Doctor!\N- Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.85,0:17:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Good...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.15,0:17:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do our best... Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.81,0:17:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I am thirsty...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.46,0:17:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you feel thirsty?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.21,0:17:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want water?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.19,0:17:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.07,0:17:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.80,0:17:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.49,0:17:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, sleep now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.44,0:17:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I will turn off the light now\Nso don't be surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.93,0:17:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.73,0:17:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He sleeps deeply.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.78,0:18:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I kept changing, it was still hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.73,0:18:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.84,0:18:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's time to measure his temperature!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.60,0:18:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Lassie, for waking me up...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.15,0:18:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Has time passed already?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.09,0:19:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.69,0:19:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It has grown again...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.44,0:19:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's bad! Jake!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.37,0:19:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What to do? His temperature has risen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.62,0:19:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What's with this blanket?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.14,0:19:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Did you wake up, John?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.69,0:19:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.62,0:19:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hard work!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.38,0:19:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Jake...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.59,0:19:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.73,0:19:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Calm down, John!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.26,0:19:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He needs cooling!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.70,0:19:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish we had snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.50,0:19:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.14,0:19:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.13,0:19:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you be okay with the snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie, we must find snow quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.51,0:19:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But where do we get it from?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.46,0:19:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Mr. Nelson!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.42,0:19:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,W-what do you want at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.63,0:19:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If there is snow in your refrigerator,\Ngive it to me please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,In the Parkinson house, it's Jake!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jake has a high temperature!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What? This is a big problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.18,0:20:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.38,0:20:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Now he calmed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.94,0:20:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If I sleep a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,After an hour we'll exchange places.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.02,0:20:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So Mr. Rice is back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.95,0:20:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be a problem if the fever returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.72,0:20:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.72,0:20:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.57,0:20:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.40,0:20:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.99,0:20:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.94,0:20:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What is wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.00,0:21:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What? Do you want me to follow you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.14,0:21:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.26,0:21:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry sorry, I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.03,0:21:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Hooper!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.02,0:21:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.56,0:21:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.35,0:21:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.92,0:21:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought medicines!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.28,0:21:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie is the one who brought Mr. Rice here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.95,0:21:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom! The medicine! The medicine arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.69,0:21:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your hard work!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.65,0:21:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great, Jake, you've already recovered!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.71,0:21:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So, even you, Mom, I'm happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.13,0:21:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You worked hard, John!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.95,0:21:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but you, Mom, you always\Nwork hard and always...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.69,0:21:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Always do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.92,0:21:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I am proud because you are my mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.46,0:22:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Grandmother Forrest's son returned\Nto the village 20 years later.{\i0}
